sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Open a workspace
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/workspaces/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and workspace membership
    API->>DB: Load workspace details
    DB-->>API: Workspace found
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + workspace
    Frontend-->>User: Display workspace details
